1
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:27,080
Let me do it.

2
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:29,840
This time we need to deliver to

3
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,039
fifteen households.

4
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,410
You are a novice,

5
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:33,160
so just follow the orders

6
00:01:33,160 --> 00:01:34,280
of this veteran.

7
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,160
Okay.

8
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:38,200
Then please, Master Wangshu,

9
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,580
give me more guidance.

10
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,479
Take a break, everyone.

11
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:46,320
Come, have something to eat.

12
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,890
Sister-in-law.

13
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,170
Jiadong.

14
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:54,160
Thanks to Wangshu

15
00:01:54,280 --> 00:01:55,740
and her brother this time,

16
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,640
you were able to get home safely.

17
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,240
Wangshu,

18
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:02,680
try this.

19
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,920
I just made it.

20
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,360
Okay.

21
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,410
It's delicious.

22
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,480
Thank you.

23
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,760
You are right.

24
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,880
Wangshu and Brother Mingshu

25
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,060
both saved my life.

26
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,280
If it weren't for them,

27
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,360
I probably wouldn't have lived

28
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,620
to see you and Grandma.

29
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,650
Brother Jiadong, what are you saying?

30
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:24,800
So,

31
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:27,680
when do you plan

32
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,680
to marry such a wonderful girl like Wangshu

33
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:31,200
into our Chen family?

34
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,890
Sister-in-law, you...

35
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,000
Jiadong,

36
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:39,560
only Grandma and I

37
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,860
have been guarding this Chen family.

38
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,200
Now that you are back

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,490
and brought Wangshu back with you,

40
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:47,340
it makes this old house

41
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,100
suddenly feel like a home.

42
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,820
Grandma is looking forward to it too.

43
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:52,800
She

44
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,700
can't hold on for much longer.

45
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,800
Grandma's biggest wish

46
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:01,080
is to see you get married,

47
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,300
so she can give an explanation

48
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,410
to your parents.

49
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:05,970
Sister-in-law.

50
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,240
I understand what you're saying.

51
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,000
But as you know,

52
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,960
the situation is very critical now.

53
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:11,800
I don't know when

54
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,080
I will return to Malaya.

55
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,940
And I don't want to wrong Wangshu.

56
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,850
Just tell me,

57
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,540
do you like Wangshu or not?

58
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,480
I...

59
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:28,640
I like her.

60
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,480
That settles it.

61
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:33,520
What about you, Wangshu?

62
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,079
Brother Jiadong,

63
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,040
hasn't he always been

64
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,079
my fiancé?

65
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,800
Wasn't that all fake?

66
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:43,880
Shut up.

67
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,800
I'm going to tell Grandma

68
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,120
and make her happy too.

69
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,160
After you finish delivering

70
00:03:50,160 --> 00:03:51,760
these fifteen remittances,

71
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,600
we will arrange your wedding.

72
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,880
You can't let a girl

73
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,800
without a proper status

74
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,040
follow you around.

75
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,160
Sister-in-law.

76
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,160
I haven't asked Uncle Lin

77
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,000
if he agrees yet.

78
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,930
Sister-in-law.

79
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,000
What?

80
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,440
Why are you dawdling?

81
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,900
Do you not want to marry me?

82
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,680
How could that be?

83
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,040
Are you okay, Wangshu?

84
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,680
I'm fine,

85
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,760
Jiadong. What about you?

86
00:04:34,760 --> 00:04:35,290
I'm fine.

87
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,159
It's too close

88
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:37,920
to the Japanese Jinmen Maintenance Committee.

89
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:38,520
Someone must have

90
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,920
attacked the committee.

91
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,960
It's too dangerous here.

92
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:44,800
Let's get out of here.

93
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,240
Go.

94
00:04:45,320 --> 00:04:46,360
This is how it is to deliver Qiaopi.

95
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,640
Any danger can happen.

96
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,400
With more than half of China fallen,

97
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,120
we face an additional risk

98
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,120
of artillery fire.

99
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,680
Wangshu,

100
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,000
go back to the old house in Quanzhou.

101
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,640
It's too dangerous here.

102
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,480
You can't stay here.

103
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,409
How can I do that?

104
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,159
We agreed

105
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,920
to deliver the 15 Qiaopi together.

106
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,920
You have to marry me when we get back.

107
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,520
Brother Jiadong.

108
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,400
That should be

109
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,600
Li Tianguang's house ahead.

110
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,330
It should be.

111
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,840
I just don't know if they still live here

112
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,080
after the occupation.

113
00:05:12,080 --> 00:05:13,210
Let's go take a look.

114
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,100
Little kid,

115
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,140
I'd like to ask,

116
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:19,800
is Li Tianguang's house ahead?

117
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,120
What are you here for?

118
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,640
We are letter deliverers.

119
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,200
Delivering Li Tianguang's letter.

120
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,060
I'm his sister.

121
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,440
Mom, brother finally sent a letter!

122
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,840
I will never see

123
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,840
my poor A'tian again.

124
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,080
I've been waiting here

125
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,840
for over a decade.

126
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,080
Those damned Japanese.

127
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:43,400
I stayed here and didn't dare to flee,

128
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:44,960
just in case A'tian

129
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,960
and his letter came back one day

130
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,640
and couldn't find me.

131
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,840
I didn't expect

132
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:53,810
he had already fallen victim to the Japanese.

133
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,290
Grandma, I'm sorry.

134
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,240
It's my fault.

135
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,760
I'm twelve years late

136
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,620
in delivering this letter to you.

137
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
This is what Brother Tianguang

138
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,400
sent along with the letter.

139
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,530
Please keep it safe.

140
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,600
I don't blame you.

141
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,040
If anyone is to blame, it's those

142
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,560
damned Japanese.

143
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,360
You two are still so young,

144
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,800
taking such a big risk

145
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,410
to deliver the letter to us.

146
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,920
You are our great benefactors.

147
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,160
I...

148
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,520
Grandma, please don't.

149
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,640
Please don't, get up.

150
00:06:23,640 --> 00:06:24,240
Please sit.

151
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,300
Please sit, don't.

152
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:26,800
Please sit.

153
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,480
Come, sit.

154
00:06:29,320 --> 00:06:30,160
Delivering letters is

155
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,420
the duty of our bureau.

156
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,210
Please don't be too sad.

157
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,240
It's still too dangerous here.

158
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,840
You should move out as soon as possible.

159
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,000
Brother Tianguang wouldn't want anything

160
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,930
to happen to you.

161
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,290
I have one foot in the grave.

162
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:43,700
I am not afraid.

163
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,360
But for you two young people,

164
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,320
there's a war outside.

165
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,380
It's not peaceful.

166
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:52,400
It's so dangerous for you out there.

167
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,100
It's fine, Granny.

168
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,600
When I came, I heard that

169
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,680
the Blood and Soul Corps

170
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,400
will launch a night attack

171
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,880
on the Japanese stronghold tonight.

172
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,440
As long as our people are united,

173
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,640
the Japanese won't run rampant on our territory

174
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:02,760
for much longer.

175
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:05,520
Good. Then hit them hard.

176
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,040
Avenge my Ah Tian.

177
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,650
Sister-in-law,

178
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,160
I'm back.

179
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,170
Sister-in-law,

180
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,360
where is Grandma?

181
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,040
Grandma.

182
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,640
I only left for a few days.

183
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,360
How did you get so sick?

184
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,480
Grandma's health

185
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,280
has been failing for a long time.

186
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,560
She was holding on,

187
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,400
waiting for you two to come back.

188
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,680
A few days ago,

189
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,240
when she heard you wanted to get married,

190
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,240
she was thrilled.

191
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:47,320
She kept telling me

192
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:50,600
to prepare for the betrothal ceremonies.

193
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,840
She even insisted on preparing

194
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:55,159
the invitations and wedding cakes with me.

195
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,020
But as a result,

196
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:58,040
while she was with me,

197
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,280
grinding bean paste,

198
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,280
she suddenly fainted

199
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,360
and never got up again.

200
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:09,560
Grandma.

201
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,080
This

202
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,720
is our Chen family's

203
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:23,960
heirloom gold bracelet for the grandson's wife.

204
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,240
I've been keeping it ready.

205
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,920
Girl,

206
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,400
can you fulfill a dream of mine?

207
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:35,120
I want to

208
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:40,520
see you and Jiadong

209
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,280
get married with my own eyes.

210
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,080
When I

211
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,960
go see Adong's

212
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:49,600
parents,

213
00:08:52,760 --> 00:08:58,360
I can have a drink with them

214
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:02,840
and tell them the good news.

215
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,360
My Adong

216
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:10,880
is married.

217
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,360
Okay.

218
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:15,520
Grandma, I promise you.

219
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,560
Wangshu.

220
00:09:17,880 --> 00:09:19,740
Fortunately, my brother is here.

221
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,480
Dad will understand.

222
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:25,290
Thank you, Wangshu.

223
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,680
We are all family now.

224
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,080
There's no need to say thanks, sister-in-law.
